&lt;p&gt;The Presales Senior Engineer is a senior technical presales leader responsible for owning complex sales engagements, shaping solution strategy, and guiding the development of high-quality proposals, estimates, and statements of work. This role partners with sales, delivery, and presales architects to align customer requirements with C3’s service portfolio and Reference Architecture standards while reducing risk and improving solution quality.&lt;/p&gt;
